<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
  <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-indicators">
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-inner" style="height: 100vh; min-height: 400px;">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img src="schoolproject.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="studentsplanting.jpg" alt="" /> 
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
    <img src="schoolplanting.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
  </button>
  <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
  </button>
</div>
  
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6" style="background-color: #191970;">
  
  <div class="px-3 pt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center text-white" style="color: #00FF7F;">School Projects in Lower Moshi </h1>
    <div class="mx-auto col-sm-10 pt-4 fs-4 text-white">
    <p>Due to the lack of trees and the heat, children cannot play outside during school hours. They have to stay inside 
    the classroom all day. </p>
    <p>Early 2022, in total 2400 trees were planted at primary schools in three villages: Londoto, Kiruani and Mawala. 
    The earlier the better, the shade trees will allow the kids to play outside, which is vital  for their physical and 
    mental development. Harvest from the mango, papaya and guava trees will enrich their school lunch.</p>
    
    <p>There are other schools in Lower Moshi that are eager to plant trees, please support them and donate</p>
  
    <div class="text-center py-5 fs-4">
    <%= button_to raw("<i class=\"fas fa-hand-holding-heart\"> Donate Now</i>"), 
      new_donation_path, method: :get,  
      class: "btn btn-success fs-4 text-white" %>
    
  </div>
  </div>
  
  </div>
</div>
